title: NFL ATL: Pre Week 1 winners & losers
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Pre Week 1 winners & losers
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- recap Week 1 of the preseason by selecting their winners and losers which includes Johnny Manziel, Blake Bortles and much more.
